  Sip8-ji7-hoe7 tai7-piau2: Li2 sui-jian5 m7-si7 i-seng,chong2-si7 li2 sou2 hoat-beng5 eng7 thou5-tau7 iu5 sou2 choe3 e5 ioh8-phin2 u7 chin toa7 e5 kong3-hian3(theh8 chit8 pau chiN5). Che si7 Kok-che3 Sip8-ji7-hoe7 e5 choe3 toa7 chiong2-kim(chiong kim-chiN5 sang3 hou7 i ). 
  Gin2-na2 : (chin3-cheng5) Li2 sou2 choe3 e5 thou5-tau7 piaN2 kap gu5-leng chin ho2 chiah8. Goa2 khoaN3-tioh8 chin choe7 lang5 long2 teh ka7 li2 o-lo2 koh sang3 ki3-liam7 mih8; goa2 ia7 ai3 eng7 chit chiah kou2-chui e5 kau2 sang3 li2 choe3 ki3-liam7. 
  Cho2-chi3 : (KiaN5 kau3 tai5-cheng5, bin7 ng3 teng2-bin7). Chu2 ah! Goa2 si7 eng7 chit8 chiah be2 oaN7 lai5 e5 siN3-mia7, li2 iau2 bo5 khoaN3-khin goa2. Oh ! Kam2-sia7 Chu2, o-lo2 Chu2, tioh8 chiong it-chhe3 e5 eng5-kng kui hou7 Ia5-ho5-hoa, kui hou7 Ia5-ho5-hoa. 
  Cheng3-lang5 : Goan7 it-chhe3 e5 eng5-kng kui hou7 Ia5-ho5-hoa. A3-beng7. 
  ------------The end----------------- 
  (Tai5-oan5 Kau3-hoe7 Kong-po3 te7 959 ho7, 1965 ni5 6 geh8) 
